latestPosts.caption:
🌿 MUNNAR IN 3 DAYS – Quick Itinerary! ✨

Day 1 – Local Sightseeing 🛵
• Photo Point
• Mattupetty Dam
• Echo Point
• Kundala Lake
• Top Station
• Scenic ride through the Munnar Hills.

Day 2 – Sunrise & Tea Estates 🌄🍃
• Kolukkumalai Sunrise – reach Suryanelli Village by 4 AM & pre-book the jeep!
• Jeep ride to Kolukkumalai Tea Estate – India’s highest tea plantation!
• Anayirankal Dam (optional)
• Lockhart Tea Museum & Park
• Kerala Cultural Show at Punarjani Village - book tickets online in advance!

Day 3 – Nature & Treats 🐘🍫
• Eravikulam National Park
• Attukad Waterfall 
• Macofa Chocolate Factory

✨ Quick Tips:
• Very Few scooty rentals in Munnar – I used Sangeetha Rentals (pre-book!)
• Kolukkumalai sunrise needs an early start – reach Suryanelli by 4 AM & jeep must be pre-booked
• Book transport in advance – scooty, cab, or auto
• Punarjani cultural show – book tickets online beforehand
